init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But soon enough people start to figure it out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the mugs were still there, and the numbers were still there.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A company called Dad Rankings Inc. started selling the mugs again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: that said "You can't hide from the numbers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There was a lot of money to be made.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There was a lot of finger pointing, and a lot of blame.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And the world started to get even worse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it was enough to make everyone very nervous.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And then the world was gone.
